{"title":"Far Agonistas del Receptor GLP-1 (arGLP-1)","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Endocrinología/Far Agonistas del Receptor GLP-1 (arGLP-1)-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Agonistas del Receptor\\NGLP-1 (arGLP-1)","guid":"q9X2yNBPbLHlhM0hvgMP1g","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"0. Perlas","guid":"eoOfNoW8wsdiG0wsuokDXQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Paciente tipo: Pacientes con DM2, especialmente aquellos con alto riesgo cardiovascular,\\Ninsuficiencia renal leve a moderada, o que requieren control del peso.","guid":"QTqB-ifhuY-7SM4YISs7kw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Efecto en HbA1c: Reducción de 0. 8-1.5% (moderado a alto)","guid":"C1MruVO8uZHgglgr4SFi-g","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Peso: Reducción de 2-5 kg","guid":"nDF3QrHGdad1Mb8KJVJGxg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Sobrevida general: Mejora en eventos cardiovasculares (CV)","guid":"qbNm3aNajxR9giIkByuvAw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Efectos pleiotrópicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Reducción de la presión arterial","guid":"bouKzWupuu6xXauQ0LJhNQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Mejora de la función beta-pancreática","guid":"DPlPmq_ZYzKmzI7TjyWupg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Potencial mejora de los perfiles lipídicos","guid":"t_4lGKz4W-Drt0ciJXWLGg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"1.- Efecto","guid":"W8434m42z4u9ow7fqfvDWw","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Sistema Incretina → Moléculas sintéticas imitan GLP-1 endógena.","guid":"LJWU8TYPtFzzQnfXA9u5Bw","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Receptores: GLP-1R (receptor del péptido similar al glucagón tipo 1)","guid":"tQ5VjJtw_KrAG9uAVGH5Fg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"• Mecanismo:","guid":"okffU3f7rOV0O86TKbTREQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Pancreático → ↑ Insulina, ↓ Glucagón (mediado por glicemia, no hipoglicemia).","guid":"zDKaFPoYfRtq2F-nkJ7Jgg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Digestivo → Enlentecen vaciamiento gástrico, ↓ Motilidad intestinal (1).","guid":"uEGlHzt_z_GdquKAPA6PUA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• SNC → Saciedad, ↓ Apetito, Neuroprotección.","guid":"1uzx8W9DKXpOvRT6YGbyHw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• Cardiaco → ↑ FC, Contractilidad miocárdica, Mejoran FVI.","guid":"D_BufAKuRyK8QKZNKAexKA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"13","text":"• M. Lisas → ↓ Proliferación.","guid":"gUIE-vY1nrmPVqJQ9auF6Q","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"• Vascular → Vasodilatación, Estabilizan placa ateromatosa, Mejoran función endotelial, ↓ Agregación plaquetaria.","guid":"A-p9qsi7EQQ04eHxVwReMA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"• Hígado → ↓ Liberación hepática de glucosa, ↑ Depósito de glucógeno, ↓ Depósito graso.","guid":"N-X4zh9MdDZbnu0kxgWmJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"10","text":"• Resultado:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Mejora el control glucémico","guid":"l-kj2eX66av1nfLyP9EN-Q","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Reduce la ingesta de alimentos","guid":"mc11DWmST-Rfx2FiaVjrQA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• Disminuye la gluconeogénesis hepática","guid":"ojtArLTy8o2w81k4kaDYiw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"2.- Farmacología","guid":"trcNvvggjBJDM1Ik-QKtZA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Absorción: Administración subcutánea, biodisponibilidad variable entre 50-80%","guid":"kRTPGDR_tnjylj-bYgrFGw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Distribución: Amplia distribución sistémica, unión a proteínas plasmáticas variable","guid":"ptawinT0pQ9lbx5WqhWdkQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Metabolismo: Degradación principalmente por DPP-4 y neutral endopeptidasa","guid":"b0x9q6XsCJeU76SlDKvUUA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"• Eliminación: Principalmente renal y hepática; T1/2 varía entre los compuestos (de horas a días)","guid":"Zxb3luKloGs-ybtQmhGWjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"3.- Presentaciones","guid":"7hKkejw1BOxOZY_I0e3YeQ","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Exenatida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Dosis disponibles: 5-10 µg BID (Byetta), 2 mg QW (Bydureon)","guid":"gzhlpgqWQH4k8bprdT6VBw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• Laboratorio: AstraZeneca","guid":"NEFci5PtHzHfdVZcXUDKdw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"• Dosis objetivo: 10 µg BID (Byetta), 2 mg QW (Bydureon)","guid":"uprGOshg7anjyWAdh6ZMFw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"• Precio mensual: ~$80, 000 - $120,000 CLP","guid":"t3T9fz_nPnOVfwznA_HB7w","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"• Consideraciones de ajuste: No recomendado en insuficiencia renal severa (ClCr < 30 ml/min)","guid":"fiGhmdPmzEojp3HO6-JnTw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"• Características distintivas: Byetta es BID, Bydureon es QW, mayor facilidad de uso con Bydureon","guid":"Owd4yAJXLcnmkpW2rQwcHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"30","text":"• Liraglutida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Dosis disponibles: 0.6-1.8 mg QD (Victoza), hasta 3 mg QD (Saxenda)","guid":"Jj7M_HgNlsO4ZJ0pLij-OA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Laboratorio: Novo Nordisk","guid":"Hz7BQ_LYdYQCTugHtut20g","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"• Dosis objetivo: 1.8 mg QD (Victoza), 3 mg QD (Saxenda)","guid":"KYnC5UyBRxLMGYRdG8eKJA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"• Precio mensual: ~$200, 000 - $300,000 CLP","guid":"vuMn_63KgRec3uUbHE7pHg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"38","text":"• Consideraciones de ajuste: No requiere ajuste en insuficiencia renal leve a moderada","guid":"f9EQIY8r27vprwt5KtHHVQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"38","text":"• Características distintivas: Beneficios en pérdida de peso, administración QD","guid":"e2jp_wnblteOA-3Xb0xBiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"30","text":"• Dulaglutida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Nombre\\Ncomercial:\\NTrulicity®","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Dosis disponibles:\\N0.75-1.5 mg QW","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Laboratorio: Eli Lilly","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"• Dosis objetivo:\\N1.5 mg QW","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"• Precio mensual: ~$150,\\N000 - $200,000 CLP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"• Consideraciones de ajuste: No\\Nrequiere ajuste en insuficiencia\\Nrenal leve a moderada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"45","text":"• Características distintivas:\\NAdministración QW, facilidad de uso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"30","text":"• Semaglutida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Nombre comercial:\\NOzempic®, Rybelsus®","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"• Dosis disponibles: 0.25-1 mg QW\\N(Ozempic), 3-14 mg QD (Rybelsus)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"• Laboratorio:\\NNovo Nordisk","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"• Dosis objetivo: 1 mg QW\\N(Ozempic), 14 mg QD (Rybelsus)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"• Precio mensual: ~$250,\\N000 - $350,000 CLP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"53","text":"• Consideraciones de ajuste: No\\Nrequiere ajuste en insuficiencia\\Nrenal leve a moderada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"• Características distintivas:\\NOpciones SC y oral, mayor\\Nreducción de HbA1c","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación y\\NDisponibilidad en\\NChile","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Acción Corta: Exenatida, Lixisenatida, Albiglutida.","guid":"ZMGQYc6heGTdRjLHX8qXQQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• Acción Prolongada: Exenatida XR, Liraglutida, Semaglutida, Dulaglutida.","guid":"BlIfRIF1tIIH45UufkAMBg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"• Disponibles","guid":"i9XQ7vgm7E2bH2iEVvPUjw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Liraglutida","guid":"Y98qGB5oJv56_vcwq68K2w","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Formulación: Lápiz con dosis\\Nde 0,6-1,2 y 1,8 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Dosificación: Dosis\\Ndiaria: 0,6 a 1,8 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"• Uso en IR: No recomienda en\\NVFG < 30 mL/min, pero escasa\\Nexperiencia (1).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"Dulaglutida","guid":"DWZKdpMrWWrq14Ix5GSUyA","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Formulación: Lápiz de\\N0,75 y de 1,5 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Dosificación: Dosis\\Ndiaria: 0,75 a 1,5 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• Uso en IR: No recomienda en\\NVFG < 30 mL/min, pero escasa\\Nexperiencia (1).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"Semaglutida SC","guid":"5Vr-OtCaesYt8i6QPHfoog","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Formulación: Lápiz con dosis\\Nde 0,25, 0,5 y 1,0 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Dosificación: Dosis\\Ndiaria: 0,25 a 1 mg.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Uso en IR: No\\Nrequiere ajuste (1).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"Eficacia y Efectos\\NSecundarios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Reducción de A1c: 1,0-1,9%.","guid":"wfqGlCWhab-frnJFnjhGbA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"• Pérdida de Peso: 3-6 kg.","guid":"DhKOEi71oO5pbNx3kbqEDQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"• Otros: Regulación PA, ↓ Colesterol Total, LDL y TG.","guid":"mdRaBakD_VDzWqizXCiv6Q","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"• Desventajas: Costo elevado, administración SC, efectos GI (náuseas, vómitos, diarrea, constipación),\\Nrestricciones con retinopatía diabética activa, reacciones en sitio de inyección, ↑ colelitiasis (HR 1,3) (2, 3).","guid":"gHwR774ucrGUcGXhJFTTaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"Seguridad y\\NContraindicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Contraindicaciones: Antecedente pancreatitis, cáncer medular tiroides, NEM 2A/2B, embarazo, lactancia, gastroparesia severa.","guid":"aTRetuDk75ODDtvL56CsTw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Precauciones: No en menores de 18 años (excepto liraglutide ≥10 años), ajuste en falla renal según fármaco.","guid":"jYibBEAuv41U83gVQlCa0g","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• Beneficios CV: Liraglutida, Semaglutida SC, Albiglutida (no en Chile), Dulaglutida ↓ eventos CV mayores (4).","guid":"Y-S-HMeAdR4Y8Vz_AjUTWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"Uso Clínico","guid":"mEjsvdOIpFALawU-72kICg","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Monoterapia o asociada a metformina, iSGLT2, insulina.","guid":"2MCEj2b13ChROUOtPhGroQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• No asociar: iDPP-4 (misma vía metabólica).","guid":"m4gz1IlHv9POHOw_uNGTGQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"• Prioritario: DM2 con ECV ateroesclerótica establecida, DM2 + obesidad.","guid":"ZY8y6pcfQDP_0HfmyVYCyA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"• Preferencia: arGLP-1 sobre insulina prandial en pacientes con insulina basal (5).","guid":"JnyvrmCICf-LyYyffLT4zw","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"86","text":"Inhibidores de la enzima\\Ndipeptidil peptidasa 4 (iDPP-4)","guid":"jZ5w2_5Etk8VSgm6dls0Og","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Agonistas del Receptor\\NGLP-1 (GLP-1 RA)","guid":